### CampusMarket - Recommendations
### Run this file to validate recommendation endpoints.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Public cold-start home recommendation
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Public cold-start — verify response structure
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recommend/home?limit=4
# Expect: success=true, data array with id, title, salePrice, source="popularity", score, reason

###

### Public cold-start — larger limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recommend/home?limit=8
# Expect: success=true, data has up to 8 items, all with source="popularity"

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Personalized home recommendation
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Personalized — logged-in user with purchase history
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recommend/home?limit=4
Authorization: Bearer mock-1001-USER
# Expect: success=true, some items may have source="category_preference" with reason

###

### Personalized — no purchase history (falls back to popularity)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recommend/home?limit=4
Authorization: Bearer mock-1002-USER
# Expect: success=true, falls back to popularity-based (source="popularity")

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Also-bought recommendations
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Also-bought for product 3001
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recommend/also-bought/3001?limit=4
# Expect: success=true, data array (may be empty if no co-purchases), items have source="also-bought", coPurchaseCount

###

### Also-bought for product with no co-purchases
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recommend/also-bought/99999?limit=4
# Expect: success=true, data=[] (empty array, no error)

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Edge cases
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Edge case — default limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recommend/home
# Expect: success=true, returns default 8 items

###

### Edge case — large limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recommend/home?limit=100
# Expect: success=true, returns at most available products, no server error
